						 <p>Hello! Today I want to present you: <strong>Alan's first SCP on this site <tt>(remastered version)</tt></strong>. Since the original skip has stayed at 0 for over a month, I've decided that it would be a good idea to rework it. And&#8230; Well, there is it. <em>Hope you liked it!</em></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Critters</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Critters</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I'd like to deeply thank the following people who weren't afraid of the size of this article and gave me valuable feedback:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drcaroll" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3828846&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562367518" alt="DrCaroll" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3828846)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drcaroll" >DrCaroll</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/athosnetwork" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5012224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562367518" alt="AthosNetwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5012224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/athosnetwork" >AthosNetwork</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leveritas" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1558990&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562367518" alt="Leveritas" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1558990)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leveritas" >Leveritas</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562367518" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-warudo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5099976&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562367518" alt="Dr Warudo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5099976)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-warudo" >Dr Warudo</a></span></li> </ul> <p>Also to people who critiqued the old version of this:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1705184&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562367518" alt="Mortos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1705184)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" >Mortos</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/countless-skies" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3477314&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562367518" alt="Countless Skies" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3477314)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/countless-skies" >Countless Skies</a></span></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> 
